                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120115-34-off191 t18120115-34-cd192"></join>, one hundred and two pair of silk stockings, value 60 l. and one hundred and eighty pair of gloves, value 15 l. the property of 
                     
