                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120115-34-defend409 t18120115-34-punish197"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 26.</p>
               <p>SCOTT - <rs id="t18120115-34-verdict198" type="verdictDescription">
